<lb n="1"/>kāmanibhuṇḍu bhīmanakuṁ gāmavasānkiṁ buṭṭi 
<lb n="2"/>baṁdhuciṁttāmaṇi yaina koṇḍaṁḍu cita<unclear>ṁ</unclear>bugaṁ bā 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>mulapāṭa sajjanastōmanutiṁ bradīpakamu dhū¨rjja 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṭi kette nakhaṇḍava¨rtti yuddāmayaśaḥprakāśi 
<lb n="5"/>damatallikiṁ daṁḍṛki dha¨rmmu vē¨rpaḍanu <g type="ddanda">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">1</supplied> ja 
